Food Fighters US - Season 2, Episode 1




I'm Bringing the Spice

This week's home kitchen hero is Jacky Herrera. Jacky lives in Orlando, Florida but hails from El Paso, Texas and is one of six kids in a big Latin Texan family. She hopes to win enough money to go on a bucket list trip with her parents to give back to them for having brought up such an amazing family.




Original Air Date: 02-Jul-2015
